{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mortifera</strong> is a single-player psychological horror game that plunges you into an investigation of the mysterious misfortune that has devastated your family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/7.gif?t=1733931871\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock doors, collect objects, and use them wherever they are needed to uncover the truth.. Face the centuries-old evil lurking in the depths of the house. and the ominous, shadowy forest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/8.gif?t=1733931871\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the dark corridors and forest, your only aid is a flashlight and the guiding signs that point the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/9.gif?t=1733931871\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore various locations in the forest to collect crucial clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/5.gif?t=1733931871\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feel the tension and fear as you delve deeper into the mystery. At the same time, immerse yourself further in the game by reading or listening to notes left behind by your family and following the unfolding story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/10.gif?t=1733931871\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With realistic graphics and immersive sounds, paired with a minimal user interface, Mortifera keeps you on edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/3.gif?t=1733931871\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Developed by a team of two, the game draws inspiration from classic horror titles known for their psychological elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/2.gif?t=1733931871\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3337690?t=1733931871","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3337690?t=1733931871","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/824c7cdabac03ff61f897cd21b3b5c4427b480ad/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733931871","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/824c7cdabac03ff61f897cd21b3b5c4427b480ad/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733931871","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mortifera</strong> is a single-player psychological horror game that plunges you into an investigation of the mysterious misfortune that has devastated your family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/7.gif?t=1733931871\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock doors, collect objects, and use them wherever they are needed to uncover the truth.. Face the centuries-old evil lurking in the depths of the house. and the ominous, shadowy forest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337690/extras/8.gif?t=1733931871\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the dark corridors and forest, your only aid is a flashlight and the guiding signs that point the way.<